<section id="level-editor" class="doc-section">
  <h1 class="page-title">Level Editor</h1>
  <p><a href="#home">&#8592; Home</a></p>
  <hr />
  <p>Super Mango includes a standalone visual level editor (<code>out/super-mango-editor</code>) that lets designers place, move, and configure entities on a scrollable canvas, then save the result as a TOML level file that the game engine loads directly.</p>
  <pre><code class="language-sh">make editor        # build the editor binary &#8594; out/super-mango-editor
make run-editor    # build and launch</code></pre>
  <hr />

